high_descs: Turn to your left walk straight then turn right facing the island beside the sink
Pick up the cabbage on the island
Turn to your right walk forward then turn to your left
Put the cabbage in the sink and rinse it
Pick up the cabbage then turn around to your right then head to the island
Put the cabbage on the island in front of the knife
anns.task_desc: Put the clean cabbage on the island

high_descs: move to the end table to the left of the sink
pick up lettuce from the end table
move to the sink to the right
clean the lettuce in the sink
move to the end table to the left of the sink
put the lettuce on the end table
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned head of lettuce on the end table.

high_descs: Go to the end table next to the garbage bag.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Move over to the sink to the right.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Move over to the left to the end table at the end of the table.
Set the clean lettuce on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Set rinsed lettuce on the end table by the garbage bag.

high_descs: Turn and walk over to the small dark table left of the kitchen counter
Pick up the lettuce from the table
Turn right and walk over to the sink
Place the lettuce in the sink and wash it
Turn left and walk back to the small table
Put the lettuce down on the table
anns.task_desc: Put the washed lettuce on the small table

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the black table next to the trash bag.
Pick up the lettuce from the table.
Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left towards the small black table.
Place the lettuce on top of the cutting knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Clean the lettuce from the black table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black table in the right corner.
Pick up the head of lettuce.
Take a few steps right and stand in front of the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink.
Pick up the lettuce and walk back to the black table.
Put the lettuce back on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed head of lettuce on a table.
